IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.D_STFinanceDates') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.D_STFinanceDates
GO

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.D_STFinanceDates (
[date_dim_id] int,
[sap_transactionsheader_postingdate] date,
[epoch] bigint,
[actual_year] int,
[actual_year_month] nvarchar(4000),
[actual_month_name] nvarchar(4000),
[actual_month_number] nvarchar(4000),
[actual_day_name] nvarchar(4000),
[actual_day_of_week] int,
[is_week_day] int,
[actual_day_of_month] int,
[is_last_day_of_month] int,
[last_day_of_month] nvarchar(4000),
[actual_day_of_year] int,
[actual_week_of_year] int,
[actual_quarter_of_year] int,
[fiscal_year] int,
[fiscal_year_month] nvarchar(4000),
[fiscal_month_sort] int,
[actual_month_sort] int,
[actual_week_of_year_sun] int,
[actual_day_of_week_sun] int,


    
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Structured Data/FINANCE/stfinancedates.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.D_STFinanceDates 
GO
